studio deemed too terrible to release, a Vietnam
Veteran Sal Bando(Sorbo), tortured by his past as
a Poolboy returns home to Van Nuys, California,
and a country he doesn't recognize, in which it
seems only Mexicans run pool-cleaning companies.
Bando sets off on a brutal mission to reclaim his
"rightful" vocation and enact revenge on the man
(Trejo) who killed his wife and son.
